## Current Role

What you do now. Your title, company, and what you're responsible for. What makes your current work interesting.

## Technical Stack

Languages, frameworks, and tools you work with. Where you're strongest and what you're learning.

## What I've Built

Projects you're proud of. What you built, why it matters, and what you learned. Include links where possible.

## AI Journey

How you got into AI. What tools you use, what you're experimenting with, your comfort level with agents and automation.

## Philosophy

How you think about AI, engineering, and building things. What excites you, what concerns you, what you believe about the future.
